1.content: I started early to go to ADPROC, saw Zac and Ben on the way then had a fairly boring lecture, but watched Zac do some cool web shit! Then went home for half an hour before heading off to work, I was originally gonna do my VPN lab for cosine, but ended up making this app right here! Took me ages but was super fun to make and I think it looks awesome! especially with the jQuery stuff, hopefully gonna be a boss at it soon. Came home and had steak w/ Katie w/ peppercorn sauce! Watched some yu gi oh abridged then been sat here all evening finishing off this app. Upstairs are noisy as shit! Stupid drunk tossers!
